OL,3,CPeston: Don't believe what the market
OL,4,Cis saying about interest rates
OL,6,FI have good and bad news about the
OL,7,Foutlook for living standards.
OL,9,FThe good is that sometimes investors -
OL,10,Fmarkets - are spectacularly wrong.
OL,12,FAn egregious example in the past few
OL,13,Fdays is that prices in the so-called
OL,14,FOvernight Indexed Swap market have
OL,15,Fbeen signalling there could be a
OL,16,Fpainful four interest rate rises over
OL,17,Fthe coming nine months, to curb the
OL,18,Finflation caused by Trump's Iran war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
