OL,3,CPeston: Don't believe what the market
OL,4,Cis saying about interest rates
OL,6,FThis has infuriated the executives and
OL,7,Fexperts on the Bank of England's
OL,8,FMonetary Policy Committee, led by the
OL,9,Fgovernor Andrew Bailey.
OL,11,FHis expectation, as I understand it,
OL,12,Fis that the most likely path for
OL,13,Finterest rates in coming months is
OL,14,Fthey stay where they are. And since
OL,15,Fthe bank set interest rates, that sort
OL,16,Fof matters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
