FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774519534
OL,3,CPeston: Don't believe what the market
OL,4,Cis saying about interest rates
OL,6,FThe point is that Trump's war makes
OL,7,Feveryone so gloomy that the
OL,8,Fdisinflation from a slowing economy
OL,9,Fwill take the edge off the inflation
OL,10,Fcaused by the oil price surge.
OL,12,FThe bad news is bad though.
OL,14,FIt's that oil and gas prices will
OL,15,Fremain elevated for months, even if
OL,16,FTrump's putative peace talks aren't a
OL,17,Ffigment of his imagination. Too much
OL,18,Fdamage has already been done to energy
OL,19,Finfrastructure, and the Hormuz Strait
OL,20,Fwon't be re-opened quickly
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
