PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774519534
OL,3,CPeston: Don't believe what the market
OL,4,Cis saying about interest rates
OL,6,FSo the risks are serious of disrupted
OL,7,Fsupply chains, contagion to critical
OL,8,Fmanufacturing, rising food prices and
OL,9,Feven worse financial markets chaos,
OL,10,Fwith the private credit market looking
OL,11,Fincreasingly vulnerable.
OL,13,FTrump has been the bringer of this
OL,14,Fmayhem. Maybe don't send him an Easter
OL,15,FEgg.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
